00:38:33,405 --> 00:38:35,135
Go to Paris.

745
00:38:35,235 --> 00:38:38,175
Clear your head.
Find a nice French girl.

746
00:38:38,275 --> 00:38:40,505
'Cause you know, deep down,
she's never gonna love you

747
00:38:40,605 --> 00:38:42,305
- the way you love her.
- Stop saying that.

748
00:38:42,415 --> 00:38:44,575
- She's never gonna do it.
- You can't have her.

749
00:38:44,675 --> 00:38:46,715
- Stop saying that!
- [gunshot]

750
00:38:46,815 --> 00:38:51,515
<i>[tense music]</i>

751
00:38:51,615 --> 00:38:52,885
[gunshot]

752
00:38:52,985 --> 00:38:54,985
[groaning]

753
00:38:58,395 --> 00:39:04,835
<i>♪ ♪</i>

754
00:39:14,405 --> 00:39:16,075
Joseph?

755
00:39:35,095 --> 00:39:37,765
[groaning, straining]

756
00:39:46,045 --> 00:39:47,035
[gunshot]

757
00:39:49,865 --> 00:39:52,265
<i>Family, friends, lovers,
and all the rest,</i>

758
00:39:52,365 --> 00:39:54,295
<i>forgive me for this.</i>

759
00:39:54,395 --> 00:39:58,165
<i>But it's not like you can say
you didn't see this coming.</i>

760
00:39:58,275 --> 00:40:00,135
<i>I've always had
a complicated relationship</i>

761
00:40:00,235 --> 00:40:01,735
<i>with my own existence.</i>

762
00:40:01,845 --> 00:40:03,575
<i>[indistinct
police radio chatter]</i>

763
00:40:03,675 --> 00:40:05,475
<i>I was given
a second chance on life</i>

764
00:40:05,575 --> 00:40:08,515
<i>after the attack
in the park, and...</i>

765
00:40:08,615 --> 00:40:11,085
<i>I've decided not to take it.</i>

766
00:40:11,185 --> 00:40:12,845
<i>I thought I could change</i>

767
00:40:12,955 --> 00:40:15,955
<i>and, by changing myself,
alter the world around me.</i>

768
00:40:16,055 --> 00:40:19,525
<i>But change
is a fool's pipe dream.</i>

769
00:40:19,625 --> 00:40:22,095
<i>This world is ugly and crass.</i>

770
00:40:22,195 --> 00:40:24,265
<i>People lie, and people leave.</i>

771
00:40:24,365 --> 00:40:27,695
<i>And the beauty that does exist
is fleeting and insincere.</i>

772
00:40:27,795 --> 00:40:30,005
<i>Still, every now and again,</i>

773
00:40:30,105 --> 00:40:33,105
<i>someone comes along who will
make you believe in love.</i>

774
00:40:33,205 --> 00:40:35,435
<i>And if you find that person,</i>

775
00:40:35,545 --> 00:40:37,475
<i>don't let go.</i>

776
00:40:37,575 --> 00:40:41,115
<i>And maybe together, you can
keep the monsters at bay.</i>

777
00:40:41,215 --> 00:40:43,285
<i>I was never that lucky.</i>

778
00:40:43,385 --> 00:40:46,985
<i>So I'm ending things
on my own terms.</i>

779
00:40:47,085 --> 00:40:49,655
<i>Both: Know that
I love you all</i>

780
00:40:49,755 --> 00:40:53,295
<i>and hope we'll meet again
on the cosmic highway.</i>

781
00:40:53,395 --> 00:40:54,795
<i>Stay amazing.</i>

782
00:40:54,895 --> 00:40:58,365
<i>Love, Peach Anais Salinger.</i>

783
00:41:00,295 --> 00:41:01,735
<i>What could I do?</i>

784
00:41:01,835 --> 00:41:03,865
<i>She was never going
to let you go.</i>

785
00:41:03,965 --> 00:41:07,405
<i>- Dispatch to Nico.</i>
- Go ahead.

786
00:41:07,505 --> 00:41:09,005
<i>Ran that plate you asked for.</i>

787
00:41:09,105 --> 00:41:11,145
<i>Car's registered
to an Ivan Mooney.</i>

788
00:41:11,245 --> 00:41:13,875
<i>- Address in Manhattan.</i>
- Stolen?

789
00:41:13,975 --> 00:41:16,345
<i>No. Not reported, anyway.</i>

790
00:41:16,445 --> 00:41:17,685
Thanks, Diane.

791
00:41:17,785 --> 00:41:20,685
[siren wailing]

792
00:41:20,785 --> 00:41:23,655
<i>[dark piano music]</i>

793
00:41:23,755 --> 00:41:30,765
<i>♪ ♪</i>

794
00:41:46,375 --> 00:41:48,145
Well...

795
00:41:48,245 --> 00:41:49,985
you said you owe me one.

796
00:41:53,315 --> 00:41:54,885
You're lucky.

797
00:41:54,985 --> 00:41:57,455
The bullet only grazed you.

798
00:41:57,555 --> 00:42:00,055
[chuckles]

799
00:42:00,155 --> 00:42:01,925
I feel lucky.

800
00:42:02,965 --> 00:42:04,065
You want to talk about it?

801
00:42:04,165 --> 00:42:05,765
Not really, no.

802
00:42:05,865 --> 00:42:07,295
If you don't mind.

803
00:42:07,395 --> 00:42:09,265
Mm. A favor's a favor.

804
00:42:11,065 --> 00:42:12,705
[sighs]

805
00:42:12,805 --> 00:42:15,705
So I took your advice.

806
00:42:15,805 --> 00:42:17,705
I kicked Ron out.

807
00:42:17,805 --> 00:42:20,075
You were right.
People don't change.

808
00:42:20,175 --> 00:42:23,115
Besides, I didn't like the way
he was treating Paco.

809
00:42:23,215 --> 00:42:24,645
Kid needs a real
father figure in his life,

810
00:42:24,755 --> 00:42:26,715
not some drunken asshole,
you know?

811
00:42:26,815 --> 00:42:28,715
[cell phone dings]

812
00:42:37,125 --> 00:42:39,025
[cell phone dings]

813
00:42:43,105 --> 00:42:46,605
<i>That was nearly a week ago.</i>

814
00:42:46,705 --> 00:42:48,435
<i>It's been a whirlwind
since then.</i>

815
00:42:48,545 --> 00:42:50,345
<i>I thought I'd have to explain
my wounds to you,</i>

816
00:42:50,445 --> 00:42:52,645
<i>but you didn't even notice.</i>

817
00:42:52,745 --> 00:42:55,575
<i>I suppose I can
forgive you for that,</i>

818
00:42:55,685 --> 00:42:58,445
<i>what with your best friend
dying and all.</i>

819
00:42:58,555 --> 00:43:00,515
<i>You did ask me to go
to the funeral with you,</i>

820
00:43:00,615 --> 00:43:02,685
<i>which I think is a good sign.</i>

821
00:43:02,785 --> 00:43:04,355
<i>You need emotional support
right now,</i>

822
00:43:04,455 --> 00:43:06,355
<i>and that's my specialty.</i>

823
00:43:06,455 --> 00:43:08,595
So the fridge is fully stocked.

824
00:43:08,695 --> 00:43:11,495
I grabbed a couple Xanax
off Annika,

825
00:43:11,595 --> 00:43:13,995
just in case.

826
00:43:14,095 --> 00:43:16,095
<i>You're going to get
through this.</i>

827
00:43:16,205 --> 00:43:18,005
<i>It'll take time.</i>

828
00:43:18,105 --> 00:43:20,035
<i>But I'll give you
as much time as you need.</i>

829
00:43:20,135 --> 00:43:21,935
<i>And I know
once the dust settles,</i>

830
00:43:22,045 --> 00:43:25,275
<i>you will find
you're better off without her.</i>

831
00:43:27,115 --> 00:43:29,045
<i>You might not ever
admit this, of course.</i>

832
00:43:29,145 --> 00:43:32,445
<i>But I'll know, and that will
be all the validation I need.</i>

833
00:43:32,555 --> 00:43:33,955
I'm gonna head out.

834
00:43:35,725 --> 00:43:37,925
Text me if you need anything,
okay?

835
00:43:42,695 --> 00:43:43,865
Okay.

836
00:43:47,635 --> 00:43:48,735
Joe?

837
00:43:50,435 --> 00:43:51,535
Yeah?

838
00:43:51,635 --> 00:43:53,975
Can you stay?

839
00:44:00,775 --> 00:44:03,485
I can stay as long as you want.

840
00:44:03,585 --> 00:44:06,445
<i>[emotional music]</i>

841
00:44:06,555 --> 00:44:13,555
<i>♪ ♪</i>

